Fred D. BELL, Appellant, v. UNITED STATES of America, Appellee. No. 7148. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit May 8, 1933.

Before WILBUR, SAWTELLE, and MACK, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Upon motion of counsel for appellee, ordered appeal in above cause dismissed for failure of appellant to file record and docket cause.
